name: JRAW
body:
##Welcome to the JRAW Javadoc Center

The Javadoc for the latest version can always be found [here](https://thatjavanerd.github.io/JRAW/docs/latest/). The Javadoc for the latest passing commit can be found [here](https://thatjavanerd.github.io/JRAW/docs/git/latest/).

Javadoc for a certain commit can be found at `https://thatjavanerd.github.io/JRAW/docs/git/:sha/` where `:sha` is the first seven characters of the commit hash.
